data.description: This custom Energy Star home by Holton Homes offers 2532sf, custom woodwork, crown molding, hardwood floor on main level, wonderful den, spacious great room with a 2-sided fireplace. Cherry cabinetry in kitchen w/granite countertops, island & gas range. Upper level master bed, master bath suite w/dual vanity, claw foot soaker tub, large walk-in shower w/dual shower heads, & an enormous closet. Keeping your floors clean is easy with the central vac system. The outdoor space offers, covered patio w/a private sitting area, & an outdoor kitchen w/a 30" griddle, Traeger smoker, gas grill, & refrigerator. Complete with TV, dart board & easy to care for artificial turf. The lot offers a 50' RV parking space behind the fence with extra parking in the driveway. There are two zones for the AC. New exterior paint. The upstairs AC is 3 years old. The carpet was replaced 2 years ago. The garden boxes are connected to the sprinkler system. Home backs to the park & community pool making the lot feel like you are on acreage.
